         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184"><!-- p3l5-r5 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
           <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De ennunciatione: iudicatione: affirmatione: approbatione et reprobatione</head>
    <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>
      ¶ De enunciatione indicatione af
      <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>firmatione approbatione et
      <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>reprobatioe. Rubrica. 5.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e123">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis
      <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>c. 16. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e129">Cor sa
        <lb ed="#V" n="22" break="no"/>9 pientis erudiet os eius: et labiis illi
        <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>Bus addet gratiam.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e137"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e139"> 26 c. Os lubri
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>cum operatur minas. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e146"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e148"> 29. c. Uidisti hominem
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>velocem ad loquendum: stultitia magis speran
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>da est quam illius correctio. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e156"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e158"> Idem in ecclesiaste.
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>c. 5. Ne temere quid loquaris. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e168">¶ Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 4 scilicet de
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>chilone. Chilo lacedemonius qui fuit vnus
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>de septem sapiententibus iubebat linguam non
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>preuenire intellectum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e178"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e180"> 6. c scilicet de biante. Bias
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>vnus de septem sapiententibus: ait Ne cito lo
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>quari inaniam enim pandit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e192">¶ Socrates in exhortationibus. c. 2. Quicquid
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>dicturus es considera prius sntiam: plurimum
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>enim lingua mentem peruertit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e200">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e204">¶ Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 9. Teme
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>rarius in verbo suo odibilis erit. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e211"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e213"> 14. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>Beatius qui nin est lapsus verbo ex ore suo. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e223">/ 18. c. Antequam loquaris disce. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e227"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e229"> 21. c. Uer
        <lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>ba prudentium statera ponderabuntur. In ore
        <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>fatuorum cor illornm: et in corde sapientum
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>os illorum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e239"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e241"> 25. c. Beatus qui in lingua
        <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>sua non est lapsus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e247"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e249"> 28. c. Uerbis tuis facito
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>stateram: et frenos ori tuo rectos et attende <!--190.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>ne forte labaris in lingua ne cadas in conspe
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>ctu inimicorum insidianti um tibi: et sit casus tu
        <lb ed="#V" n="48" break="no"/>us insanabilis in morte. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e266">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e270">¶ Ambrosius de officiis. lib. i. c. 8. Sapiens
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>vt loquatur multa prius considerat: quid di
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>cat: aut cui dicat: quo in loco et tempore. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e279">
               <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e283">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: li. 5. c. 21. Age
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>ne tua tibi obijciatur oratio: quia pondus pu
        <lb ed="#V" n="54" break="no"/>doris grauissimi est propria voce conuinci. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e291">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e295">/ Li. 10. c. 4. Nescit penitenda loqui qui pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>ferenda prius suo tradit examini. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e301">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e305">¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur pamphylus. c. 18
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>Uerbi principium finem quoque eonspice verbi
        <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>Ut melius possis premeditata loqui. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e313">
               <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e317">¶ Auctor vel qui dicitur facetus. c. 2. Nec pror
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>sus taceat: sed meditata ferat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e323">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e327">/ Capitulo. 4.
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Mente diu teneat quod putat ipse loqui. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e333">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e337">¶ Mattheus vindocinensis partur. i. c. 1. Diu
        <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>turnitas silentii nutrimentum est verbi: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>male comministrat impetus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e346">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e350">¶ Auctor vel qui incipit astrolabi: Prouidet
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>ante dium quid recte dicere possit Uir sapi
        <lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>ens. stultus immeditata profert. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-d1e358">
               <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d62184-Qd1e362">¶ Prouerb. metrice. extraord vel vag. Qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>bene vult fari bene debet premeditari. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
